string.name: lekhpal_message
string.h4: Uttar pradesh Lekhpal Sangh is recognized by U. P. Government Letter No.-75 (i) 4 -II-A 359 dated November 14,1962. Now in present time the member of Uttar pradesh Lekhpal Sangh is 32237. The main work of lekhpal is land records related but now at this time the lekhpal has several works related to public welfare. This application gives the information about its member and union. This is also helpful for the public so that they can get proper information about revenue relate work and government GO. The important information about Uttar pradesh Lekhpal Sangh is also available in this site. The important Government orders and other public related information is also available on this site.
